# Q: What is the expected number of occurrences of a 9-mer in 500 random DNA strings, each of length 1000? Assume that the sequences are formed by selecting each nucleotide (A, C, G, T) with the same probability (0.25)
proba_1_kmer = pow(0.25, 9)
proba_per_string = proba_1_kmer * int(1000 - 9 + 1)
proba_all_strings = proba_per_string * 500
print("Result: ", proba_all_strings)

